<doc id="263352" wikidata="Q115478229" url="?curid=263352" title="Colidae">
<text>The Colidae are a taxonomic family of large sea snails, belonging to the superfamily Buccinoidea.

==Genera==
* &quot;Colus&quot; 
* &quot;Kryptos&quot; 
* &quot;Turrisipho&quot; 
;Synonyms:
* &quot;Atractus&quot; : synonym of &quot;Colus&quot; (invalid: junior homonym of &quot;Atractus&quot; [Reptilia]; also junior objective synonym of Colus)
* &quot;Colicryptus&quot; : synonym of &quot;Turrisipho&quot; 
* &quot;Sipho&quot; : synonym of &quot;Colus&quot; 
* &quot;Siphonorbis&quot; : synonym of &quot;Colus&quot; 
* &quot;Tritonofusus&quot; : synonym of &quot;Colus&quot; (junior objective synonym of Colus)

